  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/problem-flexible-billing-document-numbering-not-provided-for-country-region/qaq-p/13793349</id>
    <title>Problem Flexible Billing Document Numbering not provided for Country/Region PT. SAP S/4HANA Cloud</title>
    <updated>2024-08-13T17:32:41.618000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>RaúlDu</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/145964</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello everybody,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;When doing an invoicing for a Portuguese company using the VF04 or VF01 we are getting an error when doing the invoicing document.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We have created the flexible numbering in the billing document, which we have configured as follows (we had to do this step for the ATCUD implementation):&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;First we have created the FT numbering prefix (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;103283)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_0-1723562775281.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151201i024AD47E9CDC5066/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_0-1723562775281.png" alt="RalDu_0-1723562775281.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Once the numbering prefix has been created, we have created the Z3 number range within the FT prefix (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;102819&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_1-1723562775285.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151200iF27C710867EEE1B7/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_1-1723562775285.png" alt="RalDu_1-1723562775285.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_2-1723562775289.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151202i02F3D0AE2D5CD80E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_2-1723562775289.png" alt="RalDu_2-1723562775289.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Once the number range has been created, we have created the formula for flexible numbering (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;103306&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_3-1723562775294.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151203i30D358F872A4C27E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_3-1723562775294.png" alt="RalDu_3-1723562775294.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_4-1723562775299.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151204i37BC5B75CE9A4CB8/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_4-1723562775299.png" alt="RalDu_4-1723562775299.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_5-1723562775304.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151205i008DE82B90CF5A75/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_5-1723562775304.png" alt="RalDu_5-1723562775304.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_6-1723562775310.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151207iC2F1E1E8874F031A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_6-1723562775310.png" alt="RalDu_6-1723562775310.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_7-1723562775314.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151206i60FC98B7EF670136/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_7-1723562775314.png" alt="RalDu_7-1723562775314.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When creating the formula, we have created the routine and assigned the formula created in the previous step (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;103058&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_8-1723562775321.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151208iB4C6BD8D0B6F0727/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_8-1723562775321.png" alt="RalDu_8-1723562775321.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_9-1723562775327.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151210i0744B4B3D4DED79D/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_9-1723562775327.png" alt="RalDu_9-1723562775327.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The next step we have done is to assign the routine to the F2 invoice type (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;103062&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_10-1723562775331.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151211iE7217808BFC76F93/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_10-1723562775331.png" alt="RalDu_10-1723562775331.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Once the routine has been assigned, we have gone to the "Record Number Ranges for Digital Signature of Billing Documents (SD)" configuration point and created the Z3 number range (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;180009&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_11-1723562775334.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151209i567DF42FF962F9FA/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_11-1723562775334.png" alt="RalDu_11-1723562775334.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When creating the number range Z3 and the series, we have assigned in the configuration item "Assign SAF-T Document Types to Number Ranges (SD)" the number range with the invoice type of SAFT-T Portugal (SSCIU &lt;SPAN&gt;105873&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;::&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_12-1723562775338.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151212i17098F7705369606/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_12-1723562775338.png" alt="RalDu_12-1723562775338.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In the "Manage Series Validation Code" application we enter the "Validation code" provided by the customer:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_13-1723562775347.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151214i6635D67CD326A1D8/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_13-1723562775347.png" alt="RalDu_13-1723562775347.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_14-1723562775353.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151213iD75167F0DBD37709/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_14-1723562775353.png" alt="RalDu_14-1723562775353.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When generating the invoice document using the VF04, we get this error:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RalDu_15-1723562775360.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/151215i7C0DEFED8D54EA46/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RalDu_15-1723562775360.png" alt="RalDu_15-1723562775360.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please, can you help us to solve the problem?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thank you very much in advance, best regards&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/problem-flexible-billing-document-numbering-not-provided-for-country-region/qaq-p/13793349"/>
    <published>2024-08-13T17:32:41.618000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
